Name: James "Sirius" Sykes
Description: One of the Guns. Adept at deploying Turrets and imbuing both himself and his Turrets with special abilities. Can use Deploy Warhound Turret.**Can attack ground and air units**

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to move to the target area or follow the target unit. Moving units will not engage enemies.
Root.Name: Move

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to cancel all orders and stop moving.
Root.Name: Stop

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to stay where they are and attack enemies that are within range. Units will neither chase down enemies nor move to engage.
Root.Name: Hold Position

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to patrol between their current position and the target area. Units will attack enemies and move to engage nearby enemies.
Root.Name: Patrol

Root.Tooltip: Stuns all enemies and deals 1000 damage over 5 seconds in a large area.
Root.Name: Barrage

Root.Tooltip: Calls down a Nuclear Strike at a target location. Nukes take 3 seconds to land, but they deal up to 1000 damage in a large area.
Root.Name: Big Red Button

Root.Tooltip:
Deploy an automated defensive turret. Turrets gain the same gear bonuses as Sirius himself. Times out after 60 seconds. Holds up to 5 charges.

Can attack ground and air units.
Root.Name: Deploy Warhound Turret

Root.Tooltip:
Deploy an automated defensive turret. Turrets gain the same gear bonuses as Sirius himself. Times out after 60 seconds. Holds up to 5 charges.

Can attack ground and air units.
Root.Name: Deploy Warhound Turret

Root.Tooltip: This upgrade unlocks at Commander Level 14.
Root.Name: Umojan Turret Frame

Root.Tooltip: Increases the life and weapon damage of Warhound Turrets by 75%.
Root.Name: Umojan Turret Frame

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to move to the target point, fighting nearby enemies along the way. Targeting a unit with the Attack command orders that it be attacked until it is destroyed.
Root.Name: Attack

Root.Tooltip: Auto-attacks have a 30% chance to cast Fear in an small area with each attack. Enemy units in the area will run around in fear for 3 seconds.
Root.Name: Moebius M34 Terror Rounds

Root.Tooltip: When Sirius is defeated, he triggers an explosion, dealing 300 damage to enemy units in an area around him.
Root.Name: D99 Detonator

Root.Tooltip: Fires 8 missiles at enemy air units that deal 100 damage each.
Root.Name: SA-55 Thunderbolt Missiles
